  ('dietitian-moex-11238', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '排卵前，黃體促素（LH）的高峰（surge）是由何種激素所引起？ 助孕素（progesterone）  睪固酮（testosterone）  動情素（estrogen）  抑制素（inhibin） （請接背面） 九十三年第一次專門職業及技術人員高等暨普通考試醫事人員考試、 全一張 高等考試中醫師考試、高等考試營養師考試、高等考試心理師考試、  代號：11210 （背面） 高等考試呼吸治療師考試、高等暨普通考試獸醫人員考試試題 類    科： 營養師', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3799372ed06", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11239', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種激素（hormone）抑制胃泌素（gastrin）的分泌？ 運動素（motilin） 體抑素（somatostatin） 血管活性腸胜 （vasoactive intestinal polypeptide） 葡萄糖倚賴型胰島素控制胜 （glucose-dependent insulinotropic peptide）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3799372ed06", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11240', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於膽鹽（bile salts）的敘述，何者錯誤？ 膽鹽是由肝細胞（hepatocyte）所分泌 膽鹽是雙性分子（amphiphatic compound），因此可作為脂肪的乳化劑（emulsifying agent） 大多數進入腸道的膽鹽，會在空腸（jejunum）經由與鈉離子結合的主動運輸再被吸收 膽鹽分泌的減少可降低維生素K的吸收', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e3799372ed06", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
